          <title>Fugees rapper Pras Michel sentenced to 14 years in prison over illegal donations to Obama campaign</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Grammy-winning rapper Prakazrel “Pras” Michel of the Fugees has been sentenced to 14 years in prison for a case in which he was convicted of illegally funneling millions of dollars in foreign contributions to former President Barack Obama’s 2012 reelection campaign.]]></description>
